Lemma subFormulaNil : forall (f : Formula) (T : System) (v : nat) (s : Term), ~ In v (freeVarFormula L f) -> SysPrf T (iffH (substituteFormula L f v s) f).

Lemma subFormulaTrans : forall (f : Formula) (T : System) (v1 v2 : nat) (s : Term), ~ In v2 (list_remove _ eq_nat_dec v1 (freeVarFormula L f)) -> SysPrf T (iffH (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L f v1 (var v2)) v2 s) (substituteFormula L f v1 s)).

Lemma subFormulaExch : forall (f : Formula) (T : System) (v1 v2 : nat) (s1 s2 : Term), v1 <> v2 -> ~ In v2 (freeVarTerm L s1) -> ~ In v1 (freeVarTerm L s2) -> SysPrf T (iffH (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L f v1 s1) v2 s2) (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L f v2 s2) v1 s1)).
